FBIS4-32305 "dreeu121_p_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-121 Daily Report 22 Jun 1994 POLAND Senate Groups Adopt Amendments to Abortion Laws Senate Groups Adopt Amendments to Abortion Laws LD2206190694 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network in Polish 1800 GMT 22 Jun 94 LD2206190694 Warsaw Radio Warszawa Network Polish BFN [Text] The Senate Health and Welfare Commission and the Senate Human Rights and Law Observance Commission have adopted amendments to the Penal Law in the section relating to abortion, which was adopted by the Sejm on 10 June. The senators opposing the adoption of the amendments stressed that they are a harbinger of, as they put it, a civilization of killing.
